{"tid":1588341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢３個半月，你最撚記得既山埃計謀係咩？","createTime":"2019-09-22T18:27:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T18:48:59.000Z","uid":31637,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c46635b765da3664a84b8eb798b20eb31e837494","tid":1588341,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T18:27:56.000Z","msg":"我就最撚記得２個<br />\n<br />\n１。搞１８區撐員佐級魔警遊行，分化上司同下屬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n該獻策連登仔有撚晒前設，員佐級係忠既，上司先係奸既，結果山埃同現實完全相反<br />\n<br />\n２。唔好舉美國旗，美國佬會反感<br />\n此山埃計謀真係伏到痴線，如果聽佢講，向美國求救條戰線應該收撚左皮"},{"pid":"20adb35f105b3b20b8a0d54f488d371e70571ef3","tid":1588341,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T18:28:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"4e6c572b965e5413d05a12122f870ea961fa86be","tid":1588341,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T18:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9d670b1a3e6a05fe403efc6977f6ead36297d1","tid":1588341,"uid":247032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T18:34:43.000Z","msg":"binc笑一下就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如一人一個 講下呢幾個月有咩好勁嘅計策<br />\n我先：長輩圖，全球登報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710fd1665b9d6e178280c6aeb8ac5c9a99d5f828","tid":1